  <brief_title>Impact of Virtual Reality Before Oocytes Retrieval on Anxiety and Pregnancy Rate</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of a Virtual Reality Experience, Before Oocytes Retrieval for In-vitro Fertilisation Treatment, on Anxiety and on the Pregnancy Rate</official_title>
